{
  "stem": "14060.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In my previous part of the explanation, I came to the point of my father's occupation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is relevant, insofar as to understand the background of the implied and practiced anti-Semitism, which obviously existed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nevertheless, my late uncle, my father's older brother, the lawyer, was such a prominent person that at one stage it was suggested that he should become lord mayor, which of course in the 1920s was out of the question.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A, he wouldn't have accepted it, and b, he would have never been suitable for it as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nevertheless, because of his standing in the community-- in the general community, I'm not talking about the Jewish community-- and his record in the courts and so on, being a very successful lawyer, he had extremely good connections, because in fact he was sort of supportive of a more democratic type of political party.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The reason I mention that is-- besides the personal anecdote-- is that he in turn had the influence in the town hall.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father's livelihood or occupation after the first war was greatly enhanced by this fact, because as I told you, he went into the real estate business.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whilst he was quite financial, and also having married the daughter of a very wealthy person from [INAUDIBLE], my grandfather also, or grandparents, he went into partnership with two ladies who I remember very clearly, non-Jewish ladies.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were known to be the wealthiest people in town, and literally so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I personally knew them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember they used to come along sort of every three or six months to consult with my father.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe he was reporting on their joint ventures.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
